9c09a9a1-2e3b-4359-bcd5-e3285394ea2d	6706c047-2e25-43c8-b0a0-de45df569e2a	ThS KDQT.txt	Thạc sĩ Kinh Doanh Quốc Tế > ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	Kinh Doanh Quốc Tế	thac_si	8340120	2	4	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Kinh Doanh Quốc Tế (KDQT, kdqt, KD Quốc tế) | Mã ngành: 8340120] — ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN\n\n* Về văn bằng: Đã tốt nghiệp đại học ngành Kinh doanh quốc tế hoặc các ngành phù hợp/ngành gần/ngành khác (có bổ sung kiến thức).\n* Phương thức tuyển sinh: Xét tuyển dựa trên hồ sơ văn bằng, kết quả học tập đại học và năng lực ngoại ngữ.\n* Môn xét tuyển: Đánh giá năng lực qua hai môn cơ sở ngành là Kinh tế học và Kinh doanh quốc tế.\n* Trình độ ngoại ngữ: Ứng viên phải đạt năng lực ngoại ngữ từ Bậc 3/6 trở lên theo Khung năng lực ngoại ngữ 6 bậc dùng cho Việt Nam hoặc sở hữu các văn bằng, chứng chỉ tương đương.	626	[-0.10014953,0.021560647,0.0042782607,-0.020274485,-0.032067005,0.034492083,-0.01022763,-0.062845565,-0.00027400148,0.018880483,-0.016201716,0.0020844578,-0.0010952508,0.0378966,0.055082496,0.0019470952,-0.015217154,-0.017064855,-0.014041222,0.016380318,-0.043551933,0.010054887,0.036768645,-0.0076744556,0.01947203,-0.03499073,0.018989833,-0.040959813,0.026954569,-0.0031517497,0.0027398071,-0.008932534,0.03309464,-0.026949529,-0.005602346,-0.0043437667,0.0045643123,-0.014897195,-0.056991316,0.040256593,-0.023038073,0.010493973,0.014860553,-0.0058517186,0.023655403,-0.010251682,-0.029615847,-0.02946484,-0.06195383,0.014147116,-0.05421082,0.011278772,0.0329761,-0.013495716,0.004906163,0.0007358174,-0.006866938,-0.0053302413,-0.070758924,-0.005465887,0.006118653,0.018422743,0.008210512,0.02446617,-0.00080830144,-0.013702207,0.016379904,0.013964535,-0.010458928,-0.045228634,0.00871673,0.02175251,0.017260011,-0.023757052,-0.049264744,0.00095527904,-0.00385414,0.03330208,0.06930228,-0.023104785,-0.023971751,0.019152917,0.025750063,0.041909214,-0.03181196,-0.017481962,0.0020467371,0.035419837,0.013445605,0.027293004,-0.047300622,-0.018180806,-0.025897035,0.00