6d256b77-dca7-42d1-ae71-54587f52db0e	c1cafa19-1d3c-4ede-b79f-291f18c53708	ThS Ke toan.txt	Thạc sĩ Kế Toán > CHƯƠNG TRÌNH ĐÀO TẠO THẠC SĨ NGÀNH KẾ TOÁN	CHƯƠNG TRÌNH ĐÀO TẠO THẠC SĨ NGÀNH KẾ TOÁN	Kế Toán	thac_si	8340301	3	5	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Kế Toán (KT, kt, Kế toán) | Mã ngành: 8340301] — CHƯƠNG TRÌNH ĐÀO TẠO THẠC SĨ NGÀNH KẾ TOÁN\n\n* Định hướng Nghiên cứu: Tập trung phát triển tư duy hàn lâm, năng lực nghiên cứu chuyên sâu về lý thuyết kế toán, kiểm toán. Phù hợp với giảng viên, nghiên cứu viên hoặc người muốn học lên Tiến sĩ.\n* Định hướng Ứng dụng: Tập trung phát triển kỹ năng thực hành, năng lực quản trị và giải quyết các vấn đề kế toán, kiểm toán phức tạp tại doanh nghiệp. Phù hợp với các nhà quản lý tài chính, kế toán trưởng, kiểm toán viên hành nghề.	547	[-0.053234942,-0.00928982,-0.026069839,-0.011227514,-0.0066562872,-0.019254424,-0.03029943,-0.023305265,0.021735018,0.040856116,0.0055359052,-0.02822001,-0.016559293,0.034857824,0.006432484,-0.022523424,-0.0009651915,-0.019467449,0.015462805,-0.019308323,-0.01054329,0.013439683,0.0139213,0.0077249478,0.002863933,-0.027237467,0.01104556,-0.015470174,0.01228846,-0.01331145,0.021551495,0.005869906,0.0035621673,-0.023751725,-0.017319342,0.0039424426,-0.0062890914,-0.049525194,-0.023223836,0.029845618,0.04990196,-0.006835235,0.019630274,-0.004099977,0.048764654,-0.033342026,-0.044266585,-0.04586892,-0.039411366,0.013944699,-0.022812255,0.0041055935,0.07337067,-0.04325049,0.00487245,0.017603682,-0.0953615,-0.028323796,-0.058944896,0.0044362517,0.001881176,0.0117936395,-0.0027393003,0.016515195,-0.007608349,0.003928941,0.011067867,0.03677936,0.02192689,-0.03203905,0.053232245,-0.006376423,0.023185678,-0.025221553,-0.058615793,0.018641895,0.0007551106,-0.025350705,0.019184023,-0.007379745,-0.032384522,0.028664334,-0.0146062095,0.010862746,-0.01696575,-0.021386178,0.011546732,0.03544346,-0.005215645,0.021522969,-0.0345835,0.009617147,-0.019341884,0.0026982927,-0.030227685,-0.066280164,-0.0114385085,0.019883292,-0