76e6d66f-3d71-4738-82a1-564056de5aff	2bcde501-276c-455e-a006-e70ef392d6d9	ThS Ke toan.txt	Thạc sĩ Kế Toán > ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	Kế Toán	thac_si	8340301	2	4	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Kế Toán (KT, kt, Kế toán) | Mã ngành: 8340301] — ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN\n\n* Về văn bằng: Đã tốt nghiệp đại học ngành Kế toán, Kiểm toán hoặc các ngành phù hợp/ngành gần/ngành khác (có bổ sung kiến thức).\n* Phương thức tuyển sinh: Xét tuyển dựa trên hồ sơ văn bằng, kết quả học tập đại học và năng lực ngoại ngữ.\n* Môn xét tuyển: Đánh giá năng lực qua hai môn cơ sở ngành và chuyên ngành là Nguyên lý kế toán và Kế toán tài chính.\n* Trình độ ngoại ngữ: Ứng viên phải đạt năng lực ngoại ngữ từ Bậc 3/6 trở lên theo Khung năng lực ngoại ngữ 6 bậc dùng cho Việt Nam hoặc sở hữu các văn bằng, chứng chỉ tương đương.	629	[-0.03013635,0.015387963,0.00550173,-0.02003116,-0.015223611,-0.0004989482,-0.024376888,-0.033658404,-0.011636034,0.021976797,0.006804555,-0.027518399,0.002899227,0.04557096,0.024364077,-0.0067327674,-0.022506112,-0.0063562864,-0.0021443951,0.013351103,-0.030048752,0.023540828,0.028012142,-0.034001473,0.028008355,-0.034866955,-0.016069306,-0.036919415,0.009880266,0.0015553049,-0.0022359826,-0.0097157955,0.041209593,-0.03663897,-0.02589176,-0.0008877805,0.013276395,-0.03444564,-0.034138124,0.06996615,0.019082325,-0.023157615,0.015454217,0.019690704,0.037468523,-0.023290591,-0.03537133,-0.043860093,-0.053471513,0.019421862,-0.045687716,-0.00740673,0.048533846,-0.046445478,-0.034198858,0.01354555,-0.037610598,-0.0050450917,-0.07020228,-0.008709968,0.0042896452,0.019770427,-0.0014448512,0.021711225,-0.0075490316,-0.022102648,0.025784511,0.027792078,0.0064101834,-0.049486253,0.038133748,-0.015219726,0.03646899,-0.034477014,-0.06514016,0.00025188405,0.012229852,0.009651364,0.013374502,-0.03422552,-0.02831088,0.03289454,0.02249097,0.019736517,-0.02413879,-0.028209329,0.012966897,0.030018777,-0.0004993523,0.021789223,-0.047582455,0.009290085,-0.028738065,0.004834047,-0.03522