2606cde2-153d-49c3-8bb4-2986d5a96747	145442e0-0b03-401f-ae48-d34fade02fc5	ThS Kinh te hoc.txt	Thạc sĩ Kinh Tế Học > ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	Kinh Tế Học	thac_si	8310101	2	4	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Kinh Tế Học (KTH, kth, Kinh tế) | Mã ngành: 8310101] — ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN\n\n* Về văn bằng: Đã tốt nghiệp đại học ngành Kinh tế học hoặc các ngành phù hợp/ngành gần/ngành khác (có bổ sung kiến thức) .\n* Phương thức tuyển sinh: Xét tuyển dựa trên hồ sơ văn bằng, kết quả học tập đại học và năng lực ngoại ngữ.\n* Môn xét tuyển: Đánh giá năng lực qua hai môn cơ sở ngành là Kinh tế học và Quản trị học.\n* Trình độ ngoại ngữ: Ứng viên phải đạt năng lực ngoại ngữ từ Bậc 3/6 trở lên theo Khung năng lực ngoại ngữ 6 bậc dùng cho Việt Nam hoặc sở hữu các văn bằng, chứng chỉ tương đương.	602	[-0.044580884,0.014256376,0.012618887,-0.016524503,-0.024342023,0.011628367,-6.9177266e-05,-0.032338616,-0.023429712,0.032991376,-0.030197946,-0.016980829,0.01658982,0.043301813,0.049303632,0.0036963597,-0.019710349,-0.004264384,0.0053383284,0.010765758,-0.044082712,0.037805546,0.018234795,-0.022607423,0.036782175,2.7657134e-05,-0.009887608,-0.04147624,-0.008196491,0.013590704,-0.01824122,-0.009702098,0.035121426,-0.037543762,-0.035247326,-0.0073033813,0.0077651506,-0.027779777,-0.04615594,0.04342968,0.0040714154,0.0004647148,0.019630473,0.02201572,0.037626278,-0.008435925,-0.018329779,-0.03878674,-0.051711835,0.020997541,-0.041474953,-0.020398358,0.045924943,-0.046939608,-0.014536848,-0.01505199,-0.013794565,-0.0038625055,-0.06763386,-0.012643108,-0.017406812,0.02256795,0.028952856,0.03345,-0.029857067,-0.018971154,0.026120754,0.016238317,0.011895606,-0.046820883,0.023880161,-0.009294806,-0.0022453605,-0.022083083,-0.055367604,0.00782398,0.009422011,0.0035520091,0.064663075,-0.029776338,-0.03268793,0.017892115,0.022717351,0.04094198,-0.004175986,-0.038230963,0.005929264,0.011165492,0.015545846,-0.0017639492,-0.062153507,0.020422561,-0.037106972,0.015266772,-0.032585956,-0.02760161