0f4840d3-f7e5-407b-9710-422805897714	33f7f0c1-0041-496b-8494-06e25d93b088	ThS Luat kinh te.txt	Thạc sĩ Luật Kinh Tế > ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	Luật Kinh Tế	thac_si	8380107	2	4	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Luật Kinh Tế (LKT, lkt, Luật KT) | Mã ngành: 8380107] — ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN\n\n* Về văn bằng: Đã tốt nghiệp đại học ngành Luật Kinh tế hoặc các ngành phù hợp khác.\n* Phương thức tuyển sinh: Xét tuyển dựa trên hồ sơ văn bằng, kết quả học tập đại học và năng lực ngoại ngữ.\n* Môn xét tuyển: Đánh giá năng lực qua hai môn cơ sở ngành là Lý luận chung nhà nước và pháp luật và Luật Kinh doanh.\n* Trình độ ngoại ngữ: Ứng viên phải đạt năng lực ngoại ngữ từ Bậc 3/6 trở lên theo Khung năng lực ngoại ngữ 6 bậc dùng cho Việt Nam hoặc sở hữu các văn bằng, chứng chỉ tương đương.	591	[-0.06139641,0.03140783,0.023349453,-0.020517454,-0.014766681,0.013851033,-0.03361665,-0.039502274,-0.020000067,0.01820841,-0.0118796,-0.02231233,-0.013551548,0.034451786,0.027157856,0.011033222,-0.0080449125,-0.005888214,-0.00638044,0.0080522485,-0.06027546,0.01645301,0.01124882,-0.00092492526,0.032434676,-0.025549473,0.0040284395,-0.04961116,0.0030762036,0.005206213,0.014674835,0.0049361116,0.038331717,-0.045306336,-0.03649228,0.0048822653,-0.009479319,-0.013238638,-0.04650119,0.028794518,0.020919718,-0.00051104877,0.02995159,0.019848702,0.029800272,0.0034021551,-0.009556392,-0.046341456,-0.052052133,0.019839378,-0.052211132,-0.0100258645,0.061351594,-0.034035414,-0.009036575,0.00068874285,-0.0073265047,0.017579999,-0.060411274,-0.018038368,0.0015233973,0.016135383,0.018207876,-0.007593064,-0.010432496,-0.021697944,0.0110579105,0.010104061,0.0056037074,-0.038259454,0.01212604,0.0019712972,-0.009655254,-0.024561109,-0.051607452,-0.0033262642,-0.014428808,0.024850074,0.054893155,-0.038184494,-0.02510931,0.010275194,0.03952834,0.028175373,-0.015985027,-0.034821358,-0.0057990286,0.021434918,0.021692438,0.014236812,-0.058134217,0.0067063235,-0.024839371,0.01753427,-0.029664941,-0.061590035,-0