f42171a5-c131-4774-8ede-55d10dfe3387	00c79694-a3d6-4611-8628-811c8aea0f20	ThS Marketing.txt	Thạc sĩ Marketing > ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	Marketing	thac_si	8340115	2	4	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Marketing (MKT, mkt, Marketing) | Mã ngành: 8340115] — ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN\n\n* Về văn bằng: Đã tốt nghiệp đại học ngành Marketing hoặc các ngành phù hợp/ngành gần/ngành khác (có bổ sung kiến thức) .\n* Phương thức tuyển sinh: Xét tuyển dựa trên hồ sơ văn bằng, kết quả học tập đại học và năng lực ngoại ngữ.\n* Môn xét tuyển: Đánh giá năng lực qua hai môn cơ sở ngành là Kinh tế học và Nguyên lý Marketing.\n* Trình độ ngoại ngữ: Ứng viên phải đạt năng lực ngoại ngữ từ Bậc 3/6 trở lên theo Khung năng lực ngoại ngữ 6 bậc dùng cho Việt Nam hoặc sở hữu các văn bằng, chứng chỉ tương đương.	607	[-0.067346945,-0.01572109,0.022156864,-0.03174287,-0.007258583,0.030136319,-0.023707934,-0.046389837,-0.014069232,0.02506566,-0.017174384,-0.007177722,0.005733306,0.02259923,0.067357875,0.008494352,-0.003929119,-0.028982326,0.0057949014,0.009759674,-0.04279053,0.04092229,0.012361793,-0.006915022,0.041040882,-0.04404302,-0.016170138,-0.03214174,0.009165151,0.0053154123,-0.013912349,-0.033333138,0.05966194,-0.023213767,-0.04476421,-0.012225711,-0.008986592,-0.023788197,-0.032449793,0.036306486,0.018267212,-0.022083277,0.019389749,-0.0033798239,0.023136906,-0.008990822,-0.02352832,-0.045392632,-0.065304436,0.0076546916,-0.0686456,0.010527311,0.025366085,-0.039763093,-0.021970367,0.030027663,0.0059871837,0.02072798,-0.061640847,-0.009189876,0.0002389527,0.011441756,0.003787217,0.013904351,0.00376993,-0.023272764,0.008998122,0.014249492,-0.0004241642,-0.057384152,0.023609836,-0.011578717,0.029670104,-0.02082603,-0.06257385,-0.007125116,-0.016387392,0.0011365104,0.023910098,-0.03128907,-0.026728276,0.013092676,0.020903442,0.015803374,-0.0005995057,-0.04930006,-0.00070226804,0.009368398,0.019927535,0.012670134,-0.02467428,-0.012794135,-0.019202827,-0.001099991,-0.036931314,-0.06250763,-0.0