443b3eb5-532d-470b-a825-552dc7902ddd	d74a51d8-ce9c-4dfe-8945-d72df0795293	ThS QTKD.txt	Thạc sĩ Quản Trị Kinh Doanh > ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	Quản Trị Kinh Doanh	thac_si	8340101	2	4	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Quản Trị Kinh Doanh (QTKD, qtkd, Quản trị KD) | Mã ngành: 8340101] — ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN\n\n* **Về văn bằng:** Đã tốt nghiệp đại học ngành Quản trị kinh doanh hoặc các ngành phù hợp/ngành gần/ngành khác (có bổ sung kiến thức) .\n* **Phương thức tuyển sinh:** Xét tuyển dựa trên hồ sơ văn bằng, kết quả học tập đại học và năng lực ngoại ngữ.\n* **Môn xét tuyển:** Đánh giá năng lực qua hai môn cơ sở ngành là Kinh tế học và Quản trị học.\n* **Trình độ ngoại ngữ:** Ứng viên phải đạt năng lực ngoại ngữ từ Bậc 3/6 trở lên theo Khung năng lực ngoại ngữ 6 bậc dùng cho Việt Nam hoặc sở hữu các văn bằng, chứng chỉ tương đương.	640	[-0.07553086,0.021370808,0.01341523,-0.028870974,-0.0235308,0.032416537,-0.0023143543,-0.046493474,0.01832114,0.030542435,0.0021032488,-0.02189277,0.011548308,0.041713826,0.05835221,-0.01758666,-0.0021409153,-0.016873317,-0.018514946,-0.005360771,-0.026170531,0.010847704,0.05288857,0.0029781992,0.026028616,-0.029229365,0.005554913,-0.029667515,0.016032195,0.017109217,-0.003889655,-0.0131387245,0.020273194,-0.024585227,-0.0061692153,0.0062425723,-0.00048806367,-0.012137769,-0.048258007,0.04644923,-0.00045560862,-0.0015905466,0.011796761,-0.005426708,0.028366258,-0.018489601,-0.016787278,-0.036741592,-0.08720242,0.04018434,-0.04350712,-0.003953943,0.03179976,-0.040391967,-0.009018172,0.021706905,-0.021470174,0.0134824645,-0.06365723,0.002899555,-0.0026382948,0.0059464867,0.014628347,0.02634924,-0.004970283,-0.008207027,0.0064564724,0.0035908204,0.0014327748,-0.027158916,0.028788956,0.0020150223,0.019072527,-0.023110712,-0.06135285,-0.0010692051,-0.016539615,0.008268703,0.0474494,-0.027089914,-0.030025754,0.02613378,0.014046365,0.029589431,-0.029860293,-0.011620311,-0.012944016,0.017281763,0.024611803,0.017090097,-0.043758683,-0.009976407