0ecaf658-114f-4908-bcc8-96c1cb040981	f92fbe78-bc19-47df-9df5-e65aa6cc11d8	ThS Quan ly kinh te.txt	Thạc sĩ Quản Lý Kinh Tế > ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	Quản Lý Kinh Tế	thac_si	8310110	2	4	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Quản Lý Kinh Tế (QLKT, qlkt, Quản lý KT) | Mã ngành: 8310110] — ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN\n\n* Về văn bằng: Đã tốt nghiệp đại học ngành Quản lý kinh tế hoặc các ngành phù hợp/ngành gần/ngành khác (có bổ sung kiến thức).\n* Phương thức tuyển sinh: Xét tuyển dựa trên hồ sơ văn bằng, kết quả học tập đại học và năng lực ngoại ngữ.\n* Môn xét tuyển: Đánh giá năng lực qua hai môn cơ sở ngành là Kinh tế học và Quản trị học.\n* Trình độ ngoại ngữ: Ứng viên phải đạt năng lực ngoại ngữ từ Bậc 3/6 trở lên theo Khung năng lực ngoại ngữ 6 bậc dùng cho Việt Nam hoặc sở hữu các văn bằng, chứng chỉ tương đương được Bộ Giáo dục và Đào tạo công nhận.	652	[-0.07004737,0.03710662,0.011997528,-0.025016828,-0.033486504,0.027445821,-0.016601482,-0.048768602,-0.011534315,0.0059835296,-0.0093609635,-0.020940976,0.006116355,0.0424972,0.051505085,-0.0074242703,-0.007812837,0.0072226706,-0.014287215,-0.0055066664,-0.039211474,0.010594764,0.02174133,-0.0055029457,0.020369532,-0.017075669,-0.0051605874,-0.045350198,0.0034714448,0.020764852,0.010944355,-0.026395248,0.027130373,-0.026211038,-0.01992187,0.0074601457,0.022501271,-0.016094696,-0.041642025,0.055403393,-0.0011695396,-0.0023865355,0.027082168,0.02102649,0.025128685,-0.0012581267,-0.03129166,-0.043614533,-0.063024856,0.023101151,-0.055626344,0.004916047,0.037235558,-0.025480783,0.02081188,0.0042621014,-0.0065571,0.009560981,-0.06546805,-0.0030903341,0.008247172,0.007103833,0.016552836,0.005046345,-0.009490267,-0.024556724,0.016451104,0.012969522,0.0020780214,-0.03886796,0.012002262,-0.014941757,0.009912634,-0.046724208,-0.0505066,0.0010054731,-0.008908942,0.018262148,0.055189867,-0.033139545,-0.02748664,0.031116316,0.041746367,0.043422174,-0.017578924,-0.029533956,0.0011160856,0.01764305,0.01247385,0.00588548,-0.042481102,0.