f06b7583-45d0-43fe-af21-d4a169f452cc	bf05de23-b352-4ceb-bb6c-0ca51500c924	ThS Tai chinh - Ngan hang.txt	Thạc sĩ Tài Chính – Ngân Hàng > ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	Tài Chính – Ngân Hàng	thac_si	8340201	2	4	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Tài Chính – Ngân Hàng (TC-NH, TCNH, tc-nh, tcnh, Tài chính Ngân hàng) | Mã ngành: 8340201] — ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN\n\n* Về văn bằng: Đã tốt nghiệp đại học ngành Tài chính - Ngân hàng hoặc các ngành phù hợp/ngành gần/ngành khác (có bổ sung kiến thức).\n* Phương thức tuyển sinh: Xét tuyển dựa trên hồ sơ văn bằng, kết quả học tập đại học và năng lực ngoại ngữ.\n* Môn xét tuyển: Đánh giá năng lực qua hai môn cơ sở ngành là Kinh tế học và Tài chính tiền tệ.\n* Trình độ ngoại ngữ: Ứng viên phải đạt năng lực ngoại ngữ từ Bậc 3/6 trở lên theo Khung năng lực ngoại ngữ 6 bậc dùng cho Việt Nam hoặc sở hữu các văn bằng, chứng chỉ tương đương.	654	[-0.043817032,-0.002041959,-0.006992218,0.0040242956,-0.01617523,0.02430608,0.0053333165,-0.018921107,-0.013441757,0.034508023,-0.0066435514,-0.022660865,-0.002929027,0.027956748,0.01928502,-0.004777933,-0.015026718,-0.023630721,0.0013001416,-0.015544373,-0.042670414,0.046184104,-0.00044816776,-0.027326792,0.014397944,-0.020571353,-0.007715907,-0.042075112,-0.009000233,0.03396287,-0.008356636,-0.027239172,0.022664184,-0.052861772,-0.011443626,0.013401639,0.0002177468,-0.021827897,-0.035851978,0.04519103,0.031663164,-0.009670696,0.012045716,0.03390996,0.051469807,-0.014511084,0.0047127176,-0.04919506,-0.05179788,-0.001202903,-0.036890805,-0.0098065995,0.0416315,-0.019003177,-0.018817902,-0.004651002,-0.0028808748,0.017300943,-0.046742987,-0.029363113,0.01419901,0.00804414,0.015435868,0.030952092,-0.0076889787,-0.007283196,0.029432518,0.016209364,0.01213974,-0.05011982,0.05147838,-0.043338247,-0.0075602503,-0.03295314,-0.09356417,0.01593272,0.017104289,-0.009209957,0.04067719,-0.055252057,-0.021713277,0.0023836351,0.03480668,-0.019548606,-0.019963887,-0.010994764,0.02046331,0.041906543,0.022305973,-0.00