9e515bcf-ba26-42a7-a08e-0797435d1a7a	acf5d920-2cdd-4216-8727-97dfe25f21ce	ThS Toan KT.txt	Thạc sĩ Toán Kinh Tế > CHƯƠNG TRÌNH ĐÀO TẠO THẠC SĨ NGÀNH TOÁN KINH TẾ	CHƯƠNG TRÌNH ĐÀO TẠO THẠC SĨ NGÀNH TOÁN KINH TẾ	Toán Kinh Tế	thac_si	8310108	1	5	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Toán Kinh Tế (TKT, tkt, Toán KT) | Mã ngành: 8310108] — CHƯƠNG TRÌNH ĐÀO TẠO THẠC SĨ NGÀNH TOÁN KINH TẾ\n\nChương trình đào tạo Thạc sĩ ngành Toán kinh tế tại Trường Đại học Tài chính – Marketing được thiết kế nhằm cung cấp nền tảng lý luận chuyên sâu về kinh tế học kết hợp với các công cụ phân tích định lượng hiện đại. Chương trình bám sát triết lý giáo dục "Thực chất, đổi mới sáng tạo và hội nhập", hướng đến đào tạo nguồn nhân lực có khả năng ứng dụng toán học và công nghệ thông tin để giải quyết các bài toán tối ưu trong kinh tế, tài chính và quản trị.	582	[-0.073451415,-0.003966387,-0.030737605,-0.02680151,-0.009769727,0.014709738,-0.032315247,-0.005951397,0.008450764,0.029393593,0.0114194825,-0.019592183,-0.022004416,0.038120717,0.00869045,-0.0008013088,0.0030870517,-0.0027180857,0.039601717,-0.009134525,-0.0410352,0.035341635,0.013150389,-0.012579809,0.016748205,-0.01793892,-0.011959679,-0.024995515,-0.0017823437,-0.00698544,0.021233302,-0.022591684,-0.00029063845,-0.028790146,-0.03983768,-0.0025709649,-0.0056723487,-0.0137430355,-0.048194084,0.019790782,0.051315922,0.0028152058,0.018684695,-0.00420964,0.048220184,-0.020294314,-0.0386803,-0.036457192,-0.041925054,0.022783041,-0.032302167,-0.0023386213,0.043072116,-0.0122585,0.027641926,0.02251293,-0.043456517,0.0041792663,-0.053598404,-0.011889807,-0.01740466,-0.0050259857,0.016348569,0.0050284457,-0.017744746,-0.00018514109,0.01889471,0.0302314,0.01816762,-0.024048394,0.045662604,-0.015959056,0.026229406,-0.02609551,-0.04422854,0.02207857,-0.037084304,0.002831268,0.05661916,-0.0062551918,-0.042841945,0.016881594,-0.0070176977,-0.009810094,-0.035371855,-0.028291605,-0.004701496,0.058489036,-0.009580767,0.028669802,-0.050877538,0.0070012882,-0.0056223