7ef9a543-39cc-47d8-a7f3-497a0e556116	d5c2b6de-2b30-4ef9-9a3b-5b831bce4ad2	ThS Toan KT.txt	Thạc sĩ Toán Kinh Tế > ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN	Toán Kinh Tế	thac_si	8310108	2	4	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Toán Kinh Tế (TKT, tkt, Toán KT) | Mã ngành: 8310108] — ĐIỀU KIỆN XÉT TUYỂN\n\n* Về văn bằng: Đã tốt nghiệp đại học ngành Toán kinh tế hoặc các ngành phù hợp/ngành gần/ngành khác (có bổ sung kiến thức).\n* Phương thức tuyển sinh: Xét tuyển dựa trên hồ sơ văn bằng, kết quả học tập đại học và năng lực ngoại ngữ.\n* Môn xét tuyển: Đánh giá năng lực qua hai môn cơ sở ngành là Toán kinh tế và Kinh tế học.\n* Trình độ ngoại ngữ: Ứng viên phải đạt năng lực ngoại ngữ từ Bậc 3/6 trở lên theo Khung năng lực ngoại ngữ 6 bậc dùng cho Việt Nam hoặc sở hữu các văn bằng, chứng chỉ tương đương.	603	[-0.047053505,0.033942588,0.0027061112,-0.020377388,-0.0025326093,0.024401262,-0.042333376,-0.026359994,-0.021487514,0.021307714,-0.006447161,-0.015402172,-0.0016997762,0.037039995,0.024154946,-0.007786351,-0.015557462,0.002260572,0.016793646,0.016861705,-0.05585132,0.041069698,-0.001087416,-0.027748942,0.020506805,-0.011657079,-0.020414492,-0.051252082,0.0010030367,0.008747506,0.0047040135,-0.040217746,0.025257489,-0.044359703,-0.049401138,-0.0029809482,0.0037928545,-0.01752544,-0.040150747,0.043299433,0.023693476,-0.013682675,0.021624515,0.01074974,0.028735038,-0.016642984,-0.014747117,-0.050421122,-0.04620403,0.008591483,-0.052912246,-0.023593666,0.036424987,-0.026657697,0.0035234569,0.004879248,-0.002278341,0.015314871,-0.072978914,-0.038769644,0.004749593,0.02146629,-0.003869065,0.008897268,-0.0126926815,-0.03066371,0.044171322,0.017133897,0.0041045304,-0.04649693,0.0271155,-0.030489748,0.017736148,-0.028421437,-0.06085382,-0.001959354,-0.010119611,0.009907487,0.036028847,-0.033199668,-0.03213493,0.027816163,0.030052843,0.0091373185,-0.021552954,-0.038338814,0.00093819085,0.034235425,0.0025889524,0.033684026,-0.05018846,0.002750291,-0.028086632,0.01678641,-0.03468816,-0.0524082