099d1f0e-0cf3-4c58-a52b-58610c3db6b7	adf4e29c-22d7-42ff-bb34-f86bc026e424	ThS Toan KT.txt	Thạc sĩ Toán Kinh Tế > CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	Toán Kinh Tế	thac_si	8310108	3	4	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Toán Kinh Tế (TKT, tkt, Toán KT) | Mã ngành: 8310108]\nCƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP\n\nSau khi tốt nghiệp, Thạc sĩ Toán kinh tế có thể đảm nhiệm các vị trí:\n\n* Tài chính - Ngân hàng: Chuyên gia phân tích rủi ro, quản trị danh mục đầu tư, chuyên gia tài chính định lượng (Quants) tại các ngân hàng, quỹ đầu tư, công ty chứng khoán.\n* Doanh nghiệp & Công nghệ: Chuyên gia khoa học dữ liệu (Data Scientist), phân tích dữ liệu kinh doanh (Business Analyst), chuyên gia mô hình hóa và dự báo kinh tế.\n* Khu vực công: Chuyên viên phân tích và hoạch định chính sách, dự báo thống kê tại các cơ quan quản lý nhà nước.\n* Nghiên cứu & Giảng dạy: Nghiên cứu viên, giảng viên giảng dạy Toán kinh tế, Kinh tế lượng, Khoa học dữ liệu tại các trường Đại học, Cao đẳng.	763	[-0.0631976,0.020781193,-0.03541839,-0.019130837,-0.01556809,0.016742108,-0.053284638,0.007389083,0.010681463,0.016143762,0.020691728,0.00082275673,-0.010152069,0.0121532995,0.015799966,-0.03417835,-0.0031844527,-0.004681116,-0.01873195,0.003386213,-0.042333104,0.021636542,-0.0079660155,0.014874588,-0.010252505,-0.018187212,0.0017945524,-0.05165094,-0.025368806,0.0007033918,0.011335136,-0.037427757,0.0096755745,-0.011308114,-0.0436885,0.0052018976,0.0066375206,-0.016849741,-0.033414602,0.02280069,0.069423884,-0.0022158814,0.01085708,-0.018404301,0.01564403,-0.027707674,-0.012926513,-0.032920975,-0.036866456,0.0077513345,-0.03307243,-0.02406461,0.051305424,-0.030259047,0.0108143315,0.0058439705,-0.030474659,0.0062292237,-0.04312142,0.00038868422,-0.0036225026,-0.006095399,0.014581051,-0.019815389,-0.043000244,0.0060183974,0.024359962,0.012526153,0.0028565638,-0.026829828,0.05209051,-0.029475855,-0.01688135,-0.015664104,-0.04712013,-0.008027435,-0.016867125,-0.025351826,0.02977215,-0.010051862,-0.039455034,0.024135828,0.004626