df17a8b4-a27b-46b4-8bd4-5d2b078d952c	39226159-f61b-4a74-a177-396aded803b6	ThS Toan KT.txt	Thạc sĩ Toán Kinh Tế > CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	Toán Kinh Tế	thac_si	8310108	1	1	[Chương trình: Thạc sĩ Toán Kinh Tế (TKT, tkt, Toán KT) | Mã ngành: 8310108] — CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP\n\nSau khi tốt nghiệp, Thạc sĩ Toán kinh tế có thể đảm nhiệm các vị trí:\n\n* Tài chính - Ngân hàng: Chuyên gia phân tích rủi ro, quản trị danh mục đầu tư, chuyên gia tài chính định lượng (Quants) tại các ngân hàng, quỹ đầu tư, công ty chứng khoán.\n* Doanh nghiệp & Công nghệ: Chuyên gia khoa học dữ liệu (Data Scientist), phân tích dữ liệu kinh doanh (Business Analyst), chuyên gia mô hình hóa và dự báo kinh tế.\n* Khu vực công: Chuyên viên phân tích và hoạch định chính sách, dự báo thống kê tại các cơ quan quản lý nhà nước.\n* Nghiên cứu & Giảng dạy: Nghiên cứu viên, giảng viên giảng dạy Toán kinh tế, Kinh tế lượng, Khoa học dữ liệu tại các trường Đại học, Cao đẳng.	765	[-0.061019775,0.019567017,-0.036557205,-0.018939873,-0.012797016,0.016513597,-0.053555507,0.0056597227,0.009187039,0.015428255,0.019913625,0.0012730743,-0.010737064,0.0153340725,0.013060169,-0.03500478,-0.0023246456,-0.0029587813,-0.017958753,0.0013433297,-0.043302976,0.01901459,-0.009926691,0.01832548,-0.008511464,-0.018189952,0.0033551573,-0.051452134,-0.025012335,0.0025894484,0.01188501,-0.03580404,0.011338567,-0.010529657,-0.046266105,0.004663919,0.0065742647,-0.015233406,-0.033674754,0.021177994,0.06866615,-0.0036775703,0.012633793,-0.018741036,0.01731202,-0.027994635,-0.012123223,-0.03356285,-0.037797756,0.010546752,-0.032030102,-0.023857547,0.055677626,-0.028932909,0.012174265,0.0056411815,-0.033296704,0.0062322593,-0.044327088,-0.0027477057,-0.004556479,-0.005780587,0.016111078,-0.017339002,-0.041074023,0.0058704186,0.023480069,0.008329057,0.003188794,-0.026936123,0.052476186,-0.030333225,-0.0146317035,-0.01624241,-0.04564452,-0.005535036,-0.017500922,-0.023183843,0.030558437,-0.0088541,-0.040839914,0.02512147,0.007