3209c0ae-b7c4-420f-8f83-deff795d064a	873bfa63-63a0-4e2a-98cf-7568a3bcbbf9	NCS QLKT.txt	Tiến sĩ Quản Lý Kinh Tế > CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	Quản Lý Kinh Tế	tien_si	9310110	3	3	[Chương trình: Tiến sĩ Quản Lý Kinh Tế (QLKT, qlkt, Quản lý KT) | Mã ngành: 9310110]\nCƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP\n\nSau khi tốt nghiệp, Tiến sĩ ngành Quản lý kinh tế có thể đảm nhiệm các vị trí lãnh đạo và chuyên gia cao cấp:\n\n* **Khu vực công:** Nhà hoạch định chính sách, lãnh đạo tại các cơ quan quản lý nhà nước, các Viện nghiên cứu chiến lược, Trung tâm tư vấn chính sách.\n* **Khu vực giáo dục & nghiên cứu:** Giảng viên cao cấp, nghiên cứu viên chính tại các trường Đại học, Học viện, Viện nghiên cứu kinh tế - xã hội.\n* **Khu vực doanh nghiệp & Tổ chức quốc tế:** Chuyên gia tư vấn cấp cao, Giám đốc chiến lược tại các tập đoàn kinh tế, tổ chức quốc tế (WB, IMF, ADB...).	667	[-0.06630245,0.024560926,-0.015409219,-0.02623705,-0.03554665,0.01295954,-0.04439818,-0.019667406,0.027325565,0.011461853,0.023988338,0.0078382045,-0.008009301,0.031683356,0.038309965,-0.031567246,0.0015557446,-0.0087333005,-0.06062531,-0.00666355,-0.036687296,-0.0038657887,0.012193154,0.019807978,-0.0152475685,0.011877833,0.023922337,-0.023260593,-0.02727921,-0.002801828,0.011582493,-0.00910429,0.028833915,-0.010227481,-0.009006195,0.009845308,0.045796033,-0.020287594,-0.042673316,0.027729813,0.036007628,0.024889663,0.015541491,-0.010225672,0.0120515,-0.0036616905,-0.025275659,-0.024207266,-0.04506328,0.020450411,-0.04963228,0.00012394221,0.043891106,-0.017491242,0.0079842955,0.026342299,-0.044376098,-0.0031330003,-0.053147618,0.034739576,-0.021008408,0.0004518472,0.02412655,-0.0106473975,-0.028938629,-0.0029224255,0.01640913,0.006696578,0.0009768928,-0.050310433,0.035557747,-0.0270539,-0.042167675,-0.03935234,-0.04226597,0.0127774365,-0.025100755,-0.03805915,0.07281023,-0.0080232555,-0.02957287,0.021306705,0.0026200954,0.026989859,-0.057277154,-0.034125462,-0.00389868,0.0054641147,0.009551681,0.016944954,-0.0429910