e8247ab3-db30-4411-aaa0-849d1d112980	a3510efa-9142-4d48-ba56-5e6e16d8f691	NCS QLKT.txt	Tiến sĩ Quản Lý Kinh Tế > CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	Quản Lý Kinh Tế	tien_si	9310110	1	1	[Chương trình: Tiến sĩ Quản Lý Kinh Tế (QLKT, qlkt, Quản lý KT) | Mã ngành: 9310110] — CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP\n\nSau khi tốt nghiệp, Tiến sĩ ngành Quản lý kinh tế có thể đảm nhiệm các vị trí lãnh đạo và chuyên gia cao cấp:\n\n* **Khu vực công:** Nhà hoạch định chính sách, lãnh đạo tại các cơ quan quản lý nhà nước, các Viện nghiên cứu chiến lược, Trung tâm tư vấn chính sách.\n* **Khu vực giáo dục & nghiên cứu:** Giảng viên cao cấp, nghiên cứu viên chính tại các trường Đại học, Học viện, Viện nghiên cứu kinh tế - xã hội.\n* **Khu vực doanh nghiệp & Tổ chức quốc tế:** Chuyên gia tư vấn cấp cao, Giám đốc chiến lược tại các tập đoàn kinh tế, tổ chức quốc tế (WB, IMF, ADB...).	669	[-0.063737236,0.027628502,-0.015696188,-0.02409345,-0.03473318,0.007906884,-0.044105906,-0.019646512,0.025576504,0.009559938,0.022696145,0.010783097,-0.011079286,0.037165157,0.03496932,-0.030530548,0.0019315084,-0.005420405,-0.059942186,-0.007401783,-0.04080858,-0.008368903,0.0083513865,0.022135036,-0.013762352,0.010941516,0.02240711,-0.025430474,-0.024194825,-0.0020112297,0.01309491,-0.007971494,0.029702142,-0.0058183195,-0.012198337,0.010905105,0.048370607,-0.020867102,-0.043613777,0.027960673,0.035096813,0.023131303,0.017424831,-0.010005419,0.01087078,-0.004372009,-0.030450394,-0.024222413,-0.047671646,0.02162832,-0.05058817,-0.0015562945,0.04539312,-0.019121641,0.015987974,0.027239863,-0.046914887,-0.0020835446,-0.05432383,0.03347183,-0.021098724,-0.0013727765,0.023447923,-0.008086334,-0.030988526,-0.00302701,0.014011966,0.0063579343,-0.0014144697,-0.048333295,0.03460238,-0.026932085,-0.039357048,-0.039759886,-0.040522415,0.012995076,-0.023337226,-0.035242975,0.07158797,-0.006232926,-0.03057883,0.022074891,0.0056082294,0.029211132,-0.059504636,-0.035293587,-0.002830997,0.0014697274,0.010683715,0.014681159,-0.042