dcc1c4dd-dace-46c1-bde8-b88a5a03bcd0	033f39cc-7b10-40e8-b1a4-f9c72401a03e	NCS QTKD gop y.txt	Tiến sĩ Quản Trị Kinh Doanh > CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	Quản Trị Kinh Doanh	tien_si	9340101	3	3	[Chương trình: Tiến sĩ Quản Trị Kinh Doanh (QTKD, qtkd, Quản trị KD) | Mã ngành: 9340101]\nCƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP\n\nSau khi tốt nghiệp, Tiến sĩ ngành Quản trị kinh doanh có thể đảm nhiệm các vị trí lãnh đạo chiến lược và chuyên gia hàng đầu:\n\n* **Khu vực doanh nghiệp:** Nhà lãnh đạo cấp cao (CEO, Chủ tịch HĐQT), Giám đốc chiến lược tại các tập đoàn đa quốc gia, tổng công ty lớn.\n* **Khu vực tư vấn & Chính sách:** Chuyên gia tư vấn quản trị cao cấp, nhà hoạch định chính sách kinh tế - kinh doanh tại các cơ quan quản lý nhà nước và tổ chức quốc tế.\n* **Khu vực giáo dục & nghiên cứu:** Giảng viên, Nghiên cứu viên tại các trường Đại học, Học viện và Viện nghiên cứu trong và ngoài nước.	684	[-0.06707945,0.0151100475,-0.018637381,-0.029200446,-0.032287266,0.00934596,-0.035750143,-0.02371939,0.05777544,0.03175875,0.032882895,0.007042118,-0.0028876422,0.029101275,0.028988464,-0.034636248,0.0040603965,-0.035236772,-0.057510424,0.0052023535,-0.024802502,-0.0079005435,0.033906873,0.04645184,0.0042435783,0.006380364,0.036792416,-0.014254309,-0.016424,-0.001519183,-0.001018247,0.002809724,-0.0022537766,0.0006775119,-0.0033618056,0.004988942,0.02864836,-0.022702584,-0.04349536,0.008389606,0.03415196,0.030231642,0.002255105,-0.048750583,-0.006038808,-0.026909057,-0.014889482,-0.014913188,-0.061612315,0.035178065,-0.038396522,0.0012318502,0.03267465,-0.038298003,-0.004262376,0.045009095,-0.054217473,0.0031991953,-0.043729555,0.041967355,-0.024281768,0.0019365315,0.028174337,-0.001977623,-0.02389437,0.008262785,-0.0005936003,0.014113196,-0.0022044329,-0.039975956,0.050665967,-0.0050162803,-0.03461849,-0.022314092,-0.053509105,0.013485671,-0.018349707,-0.038874928,0.053532258,-0.01869162,-0.027885102,0.008218756,-0.017564924,0.013269876,-0.058785673,-0.011462956,-0.024841523,0.01443717