8d713875-afbe-4bba-ba59-daac37dee1a7	308ab7f5-dcb3-4852-b5e4-7c586775a38d	NCS QTKD gop y.txt	Tiến sĩ Quản Trị Kinh Doanh > CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP	Quản Trị Kinh Doanh	tien_si	9340101	1	1	[Chương trình: Tiến sĩ Quản Trị Kinh Doanh (QTKD, qtkd, Quản trị KD) | Mã ngành: 9340101] — CƠ HỘI NGHỀ NGHIỆP\n\nSau khi tốt nghiệp, Tiến sĩ ngành Quản trị kinh doanh có thể đảm nhiệm các vị trí lãnh đạo chiến lược và chuyên gia hàng đầu:\n\n* **Khu vực doanh nghiệp:** Nhà lãnh đạo cấp cao (CEO, Chủ tịch HĐQT), Giám đốc chiến lược tại các tập đoàn đa quốc gia, tổng công ty lớn.\n* **Khu vực tư vấn & Chính sách:** Chuyên gia tư vấn quản trị cao cấp, nhà hoạch định chính sách kinh tế - kinh doanh tại các cơ quan quản lý nhà nước và tổ chức quốc tế.\n* **Khu vực giáo dục & nghiên cứu:** Giảng viên, Nghiên cứu viên tại các trường Đại học, Học viện và Viện nghiên cứu trong và ngoài nước.	686	[-0.06421323,0.014622969,-0.01958544,-0.029962532,-0.031466883,0.006706016,-0.03373001,-0.026229385,0.056533437,0.031668086,0.029080085,0.009069368,-0.0065585934,0.034649942,0.026679961,-0.035455313,0.001516639,-0.03388163,-0.056095842,0.0025932854,-0.026388641,-0.015018157,0.03236882,0.047296375,0.0071047037,0.0063324794,0.03525679,-0.015215281,-0.013701493,-0.0022524712,-0.0011852421,0.0051696617,-0.0019656143,0.003720791,-0.003769514,0.008577444,0.02995488,-0.022721693,-0.043906026,0.007961304,0.034223482,0.029509066,0.0021493523,-0.050582398,-0.0064831506,-0.026331583,-0.017316425,-0.016330052,-0.064003095,0.037754558,-0.039560556,-0.00060393877,0.034554586,-0.040894482,-0.002670491,0.045238044,-0.05675309,0.0037548074,-0.045902036,0.038409695,-0.02353183,0.00079055666,0.024264913,0.0017148895,-0.025408305,0.009718482,-0.004354424,0.010319262,-0.0040148483,-0.036826674,0.05146053,-0.00571755,-0.030153539,-0.022298051,-0.04923492,0.012123234,-0.01741576,-0.036040008,0.05352933,-0.018110823,-0.028309332,0.010994126,-0.016061822,0.013874726,-0.06059837,-0.009834392,-0.023071894,0.0127